485
00:47:47,520 --> 00:47:48,650
Poďme do postele.

486
00:47:50,590 --> 00:47:52,310
Ešte sa rozprávajme.

487
00:47:52,310 --> 00:47:54,360
Budeme dlhý čas od seba.

488
00:47:54,360 --> 00:47:56,690
Ďalší dôvod, aby sme boli spolu.

489
00:47:57,250 --> 00:47:58,480
Zadrž.

490
