667
00:59:28,520 --> 00:59:30,000
Samozrejme.

668
00:59:30,000 --> 00:59:33,000
Naša Kyung Ja nie je ako každá iná Kyung Ja.

669
00:59:33,000 --> 00:59:36,380
Keby nebolo našej Kyung Jae,
